  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Barista",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Sarnie Pte Ltd</p><p>We are an Australian run cafe with a reputation for some of the best coffee and food in Singapore. We are always looking for staff who are passionate about what they do, work hard but have fun at the same time.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will take customer orders and prepare a variety of hot and cold beverages, maintain cleanliness of equipment and work areas, manage inventory by ordering and receiving supplies, and assist customers in selecting coffee options.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Take customer orders accurately and prepare hot and cold beverages including coffee, espresso drinks, blended coffees, and teas to meet quality standards</li><li>Clean coffee machines, utensils, work areas, and other equipment daily to maintain hygiene and operational efficiency</li><li>Monitor inventory levels and order stock supplies to ensure uninterrupted service</li><li>Receive and verify stock deliveries to maintain accurate inventory records</li><li>Greet customers warmly and assist them in choosing coffee beverages that suit their preferences</li><li>Work efficiently in a fast-paced environment while maintaining excellent communication with team members and customers</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate barista skills relevant to the coffee service industry</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Exhibit friendly and outgoing interpersonal skills to enhance customer experience</li><li>Communicate clearly and effectively with customers and team members</li></ul>",
